title: Exclusive: Dental tech startup Toothsi raises Rs 100 Cr led by IIFL - Entrackr
content: Exclusive: Dental tech startup Toothsi raises Rs 100 Cr led by IIFL  Entrackr
description: Mumbai-based dental tech startup Toothsi has raised Rs 100 crore or a little over $13 million in a fresh tranche led by IIFL.
